{"tid":474204,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩大家留意下呢條友","createTime":"2017-11-20T03:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T16:37:57.000Z","uid":80936,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"331a59e351bb21a0abe195ea3b48b20b7f28d9da","tid":474204,"uid":80936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:02:23.000Z","msg":"大家識唔識『<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>5615 8330</strong></span>』呢個電話嘅持有人？<br />\n<br />\n入咗數唔出貨，上網搵一搵先發現原來係積犯黎， 好多人中過伏，希望搵到佢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n差佬唔做嘢，只好麻煩大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔係想拎返啲錢，只係想佢唔好以為每一次都會成功冇事，為咗避免更多人受害，麻煩曬大家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有關對話紀錄一陣間再post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為我都只係睇唔過眼，代人開post。"},{"pid":"b197988400b6820cf895475b61ee80916689bb8d","tid":474204,"uid":80936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:04:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48cad326a8218884caf80071c79aab16ee4e8d87","tid":474204,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:04:36.000Z","msg":"條友呃人都唔轉下個電話號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c4c32d711b008c04087b08a832a15b1ceea108","tid":474204,"uid":80936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"係， 所以先至可以用呢個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6a652ce4da25f6dcd534e9602d578bc1da0b7f","tid":474204,"uid":80936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:10:27.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"13f6c4e07d830c90e19cfbbd749eeb62f5a2ec50","tid":474204,"uid":80936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:49:53.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本人？"